getTzOffsetForDate()

getTzOffsetForDate( $timezonesarray,  $tzid,  $timestamp) : \LibMelanie\Lib\array,

Returns array with the offset information from UTC for a (UTC) datetime/timestamp in the timezone, according to the VTIMEZONE information in the input array.

$param array $timezonesarray, output from function getTimezonesAsDateArrays (below) $param string $tzid, time zone identifier $param mixed $timestamp, timestamp or a UTC datetime (in array format)

Parameters

$timezonesarray
$tzid
$timestamp

Returns
